        boolean sourceOfficeFloor​(CompileContext compileContext)

        Sources the OfficeFloor into this OfficeFloorNode.

        This will only source the top level OfficeSection.

        Parameters:
        compileContext - CompileContext.
        Returns:
        true if successfully sourced. Otherwise false with issue reported to the CompilerIssues.
